{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>An ensemble of heroes stumble into a creaky room, seemingly unguarded. They notice a silhouette in the dark room; linen cloth draped over a large object. They remove the cloth revealing a strange device of metal gizmos and gadgets. Upon the press of the button &amp; the flick of a switch, the heroes are drawn into the device, emerging as shorter...stubbier versions of themselves.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Welcome to Pinball Hero.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game is a reimagining of the Pinball genre, mixed with rogue-lite elements. Bump, hack &amp; slash enemy bumpers with your Pinball Hero. Acquire new items and explore mysterious dungeons. Though a hero may fall in battle many times; determination, skill and powerful artifacts will ensure that future attempts to reclaim your hero spirit are successful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bump, bop and bash a multitude of <strong>enemies and bosses</strong>, inspired by retro and contemporary fantasy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/extras/PBH_Minecart.gif?t=1739352719\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fill your backpack to the brim with over <strong>100 unique items</strong> that automatically trigger to augment your pinball battle experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/extras/PBH_Gargantaurus.gif?t=1739352719\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play against Grubfoot the cheeky goblin merchant in 5 retro inspired <strong>minigames</strong>, including plinko, slots, cards &amp; more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/extras/PBH_Graggle_02.gif?t=1739352719\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make your Pinball Heroes legendary by augmenting them with rare and\u00a0<strong>powerful loot</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/extras/PBH_Items_02.gif?t=1739352719\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Groove out to a full <strong>OST of unique 8-bit bangers</strong>, passionately crafted by the Devs &amp; New Zealand talent, Jonny Dyas.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/extras/PBH_Animations.gif?t=1739352719\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739352719","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/page.bg.jpg?t=1739352719","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739352719","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009440/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739352719","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>An ensemble of heroes stumble into a creaky room, seemingly unguarded. They notice a silhouette in the dark room; linen cloth draped over a large object. They remove the cloth revealing a strange device of metal gizmos and gadgets. Upon the press of the button &amp; the flick of a switch, the heroes are drawn into the device, emerging as shorter...stubbier versions of themselves.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Welcome to Pinball